g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedfb113e417d37d57d952fdbb1de2bf33172b17","tid":277492,"uid":57117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一堂開到20km/h 覺得好快</blockquote><br />\n一開波你要同時留意好多野，e.g攞軚,線位,望鏡,油門,入波，路面情況<br />\n同時間兼顧好多野，所以你咪覺得20都快，<br />\n到你日後有牌開熟左，好多野都變自然手勢，<br />\n剩係留意路面狀況就得，到時咪開快左都唔覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊張到轉線冇望鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b56d9510f6eab3508edcc0f98426bdde59f84c5","tid":277492,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"考車有邊條路要上高速<br />\n不嬲巿區所有車都係限50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb969ba64aeb172dd78768a034891971e42128f1","tid":277492,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有限速咩</blockquote><br />\n冇記錯限50</blockquote><br />\n屌咁條路係50唔通你行100比你pass? 考得車都係成年人，唔通所有技巧都要人捉住你隻手教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋有啲路限70你可以揸快都pass，我考嗰時都揸65 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6228ef9e1d8ae2977ff1f39a6e3b51b13b0f3a","tid":277492,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:12:02.000Z","msg":"識撚唔識呀你<br />\n市區小路限速50<br />\n你學車考車唔係50以下咪即係超速咯<br />\n唔通超速都俾你pass咩"}]}